        </figure><br><figure>
        <img src="https://media.dwnews.net/dw/xZ0pIB6FS285up_8ZbsimkqiTEs%3D/320*0/media/images/dw/43765692741a9345660803bc1efb454e.jpg" alt="船上共有船员21人，皆由海保出动飞机救起。（AP）" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
